    "topic": "2. Root Word - Mal",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Mal → Bad, Evil (बुरा, बुराई)",
        "content": "• MEANING:- bad, evil (Latin origin)\n• अर्थ:- बुरा, बुराई (लैटिन)\n\n• EXAMPLES:-\n\n1. Malice = mal (bad) + ice (state) → evil intention (दुर्भावना)\n\n2. Maltreat = mal (bad) + treat (handle) → treat badly (दुर्व्यवहार करना)\n\n3. Malfunction = mal (bad) + function (working) → working badly (खराब कार्य करना)\n\n4. Dismal = dis (apart) + mal (bad) → gloomy situation (निराशाजनक स्थिति)\n\n5. Maleficent = mal (bad) + fic (do/make) → one who does harm (हानिकारक)\n\n• NOTE:- Words with 'mal' root mostly give a negative meaning.\n• नोट:- 'mal' मूल वाले शब्द अधिकतर नकारात्मक अर्थ देते हैं।"
